# `@plop/jobs`

Trigger.dev job definitions.

## Conventions

- Keep tasks idempotent; expect retries (see `trigger.config.ts`).
- Avoid long-running work on the request thread; delegate to jobs where appropriate.
- Keep job IDs stable; changing IDs breaks deduping/history.

